headline: Totino’s™ Pizza Rolls™ Announces Big Game Ad Debut as General Mills Returns to Football’s Biggest Night After More Than a Decade
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, December 10, 2024--On February 9, Totino’s Pizza Rolls will tackle the 2025 Big Game with a touchdown-worthy debut. For the first time, football fans will see Totino’s Pizza Rolls in prime time on sport’s biggest night, marking General Mills’ return to the Big Game after more than a decade.

headline: United Natural Foods (UNFI) Beats Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: United Natural (UNFI) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 1,500% and 3.30%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
